dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents hydrography for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2010. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Calumet_HydroPoly_2010.gdb.
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated in fall of 2017 to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use.Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://www.calumetmaps.com/data.html
